## API Reference

### Auth

```
POST   /api/auth/register    Create account
POST   /api/auth/login       Get JWT token
GET    /api/auth/me          Current user info (requires token)
```

### Transactions

```
GET    /api/transactions                           List with pagination + filters (ANALYST, ADMIN)
GET    /api/transactions/:id                       Single record (ANALYST, ADMIN)
POST   /api/transactions                           Create record (ADMIN only)
PATCH  /api/transactions/:id                       Update record (ADMIN only)
DELETE /api/transactions/:id                       Soft delete (ADMIN only)
```

**Supported query filters:**
```
?type=INCOME|EXPENSE
?category=Salary
?startDate=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z
?endDate=2024-12-31T00:00:00Z
?page=1&limit=10
```

### Dashboard

```
GET    /api/dashboard/summary    Aggregated analytics (all authenticated roles)
```

Response includes: `totalIncome`, `totalExpenses`, `netBalance`, `categoryBreakdown`, `recentActivity`, `monthlyTrends`

### Users (Admin only)

```
GET    /api/users           List all users
PATCH  /api/users/:id       Update role or active status
DELETE /api/users/:id       Soft deactivate user
```

